[05/01/2018 18:30:46] <font color="#ffffff">Va,</font>
[05/01/2018 18:30:47] <font color="#ffffff">vamos allá.</font>
[05/01/2018 18:30:59] <font color="#ffffff">Tráela muerta.</font>
